arts.ttl: Breum hattrick leads Go Ahead to victory at Fortuna Sittard
arts.sum: Jakob Breum netted a hattrick as Go Ahead Eagles started 2025 with a 3-0 win at Fortuna Sittard. The first Eredivisie game of the year was delayed due to a number of fireworks from the stands.
